o a reusable Spring\n@Component so they can be called from any entry point that accepts\nadmin-supplied client definitions (REST CRUD now; a metadata-import\nhook later, if/when we add one).\n\n- OAuth2Constants consolidates SYSTEM_REGISTRAR_CLIENTID and the\n  NAME_MAX_LENGTH constant. OAuth2DcrService keeps a @Deprecated\n  re-export of its previous constant for any out-of-tree callers.\n- OAuth2ClientAdminValidator owns: rejectReservedClientId,\n  rejectIfSystemRegistrar, validateGrantTypes, validateRedirectUris,\n  defaultNameFromClientId, preserveNameOnUpdate.\n- OAuth2ClientController shrinks to the parts that are genuinely\n  pipeline-specific: the authority gate, pre-hooks that call the\n  validator, the list filter, and the delete guard (delete doesn't\n  flow through the bundle pipeline, so it stays on the controller).\n\nNo behavior change; tests unchanged and still green.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 (1M context) \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e\nSigned-off-by: Morten Svanaes \u003cmsvanaes@dhis2.org\u003e","author":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"msvanaes@dhis2.org"},"id":"a9772f1adfa905c9db513fca29ac5aedfe5383d9","tree_id":"f22c58ee77d3bcb7caf243299d03e4a808ef2219","timestamp":"2026-04-21T18:04:24Z","committer":{"name":"Morten Svanaes","email":"msvanaes@dhis2.org"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/10954","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com